{"tid":2054393,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"要預防下一間國際企業奶共，唔該而家開始做野","createTime":"2020-06-07T06:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:15:46.000Z","uid":95138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f76ea364cf5db3fb896414a124bad3e37cca5f1","tid":2054393,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"匯豐正式宣佈係藍店<br />\n<br />\n全世界上twitter 公開佢奶共資訊，呼籲全世界人BOYCOTT 佢<br />\n<br />\n1）永不用佢銀行服務<br />\n2）賣晒佢d股票<br />\n<br />\n記得tag<br />\n#BoycottHSBC @HSBC<br />\n<br />\n點解咁做？ 要預防下一間國際企業出黎奶共！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次如果痛擊到匯豐，下一間國際企業講嘅就會係， 我怕失去全世界70億人口市場， 而吾敢為14億人口市場奶共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pwZ7SO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pwZ7SO.jpg&h=1144aac0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99ba06a6829199a2d5fb713da7999a328548030e","tid":2054393,"uid":310914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"你坐咗幾耐？宜家先知匯豐係藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54829a90d47ec3f35358e417148094f626bc5d9","tid":2054393,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"以後叫上海汇丰银行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9103c9b7c35cc093588024e93c9be0f8fc5214cd","tid":2054393,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99ba06a682919